<h2 p align="center">X</h2>
<h2 p align="center">Postword</h2>
What was the world like before? What did the Initiative do? Am I suggesting the Initiative created God? What is the purpose of this book? These are all fantastic questions, and I eagerly await your answers. Or if you've been reading differently, you want to know the precise moment the Law, Truth, God, <i>reality </i> was killed in such a way... Or you want to know how a tired old thing such as myself has time to put jokes like this together. Or, how I alone know the world was different before?
More questions will just leave your brain in a tangle, but people can't help themselves. People are always concocting new recipes. I am always gorging on questions, and I am always in the mood for a bite. In the meantime I plant the seeds of worry to reap in these new, fertile fields.`
